Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:48.70,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(240,386)\3a&H5F&}{\fad(871,2052)}{\t(3457,5660,\bord10)}Evening Shower
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get a good rest on your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look so out of it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to fix yourself up for the events at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still brooding over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your break-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.62,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,In truth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:51.25,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I don't have any regrets or attachments about getting dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:03:01.04,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever felt a yearning for someone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.32,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm terrible at getting the gist of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But usually I'm pretty calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do about today's after-party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chief said it's on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made a promise today so I'll be leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A movie. I'm watching a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it with Nanoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't help it. She forced me to promise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You just go and drink with the chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before when we had a meeting here didn't you flirt with a high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flirt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Idiot! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Nanoka-chan wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just say she was your sister in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odagiri. Help me carry this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean flirting with Nanoka san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like it's so unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had a beard this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to look clean for our events or else we would get scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This movie is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you spacing out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take out your student ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go buy the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he thinking, making you come home all alone at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it doesn't matter; just go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went off somewhere on his way home right after the movie ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did that bum go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your uniform's going to get wrinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I ever told you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she's my younger sister whom I've been living apart from until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know my parents are divorced right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she's been with my mom the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been living together since this spring because her high school is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you had something to tell me so I was wondering what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to think I started going after high school girls after I got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so like you to worry about stupid appearances and dating high school girls though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll never come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you eaten yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.34,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, a stupid thought passed through my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:57.47,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, it's been 3 months since I last had sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who cares because you can drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is! You're way stronger than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my favorite restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:10:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I come here a lot by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not stupid. I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't joke around about things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about Sachiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's just a friend..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's work been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used to always tell me that you wanted to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would forget after listening to you complain so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you weren't listening with your half-hearted replies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how is your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normal I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you have an event today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or did you shave your beard because your high school girlfriend told you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm saying she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if any taxis would come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you go a little further you'll come to the main street. It'll be easier to find one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm moving next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting my job too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although thats a little later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, my boyfriend is coming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a very good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Best of luck to you, Koshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.93,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What should we do afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.21,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I didn't say anything stupid like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.42,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stay up too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:51.50,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going out with her just for the sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:57.70,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Have you ever felt a yearning for someone from the bottom of your heart, Koshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:08.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,But I don't think it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:15.00,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Is it that big of a deal to fall in love with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:27.46,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Is yearning something you can brag about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:17:01.31,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to "yearn" anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for suddenly barging in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The movie,
